notes.note:
Hey guys,

 

We have a customer here with their 2018 Crosstrek for service, and also made mention of a “humming” type noise coming from vehicle.  Upon inspection and our road test, it was determined that BOTH rear wheel bearings as well as the Left Front Wheel bearing are worn and making noise.

 

The estimate includes all 3 bearings being replaced and at a discounted amount to stay within the max bearing price of $250 per bearing.

 

Please advise as soon as you can if we can proceed with replacement so that we may update the customer if their vehicle needs to stay overnight.
notes.content:
Hey guys,



We have a customer here with their 2018 Crosstrek for service, and also made mention of a “humming” type noise coming from vehicle. Upon inspection and our road test, it was determined that BOTH rear wheel bearings as well as the Left Front Wheel bearing are worn and making noise.



The estimate includes all 3 bearings being replaced and at a discounted amount to stay within the max bearing price of $250 per bearing.



Please advise as soon as you can if we can proceed with replacement so that we may update the customer if their vehicle needs to stay overnight.

notes.note:
Hey Craig,

 

Yes, all 3 are creating the noise – he’s had it driven up on the hoist and used his stethoscope on all the corners.   The bearings are worn, but they haven’t actually separated from the hub in terms of play.

 

Are okay to proceed?
notes.content:
Hey Craig,



Yes, all 3 are creating the noise – he’s had it driven up on the hoist and used his stethoscope on all the corners. The bearings are worn, but they haven’t actually separated from the hub in terms of play.



Are okay to proceed?
